  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Modifies the tax law to include elective cosmetic surgery as a taxable service; but not including, reconstructive procedures necessary to treat congenital anomalies, developmental abnormalities, trauma, infection, or disease."
